OL,4,CElisabetta Belloni: Italy appoints
OL,5,Cfirst female spy chief
OL,6, A former ambassador has been named as
OL,7, the first woman to lead Italy's secret
OL,8, services.
OL,10,FPrime Minister Mario Draghi announced
OL,11,Fhis choice of Elisabetta Belloni as
OL,12,Fhead of the Department of Information
OL,13,FSecurity (DIS) on Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe department oversees the country's
OL,16,Fforeign and domestic intelligence
OL,17,Fservices and reports directly to the
OL,18,FItalian government.
OL,20,FMs Belloni, 63, has a long career of
OL,21,Ffirsts.
